Index	Name	BirthYear	DescriptionText
5001	Dan Snyder	1978	Compassionate, sensitive, self-sacrificing, gentle, and intuitive. Yet, escapism, impracticality, hypersensitivity, or gullibility may sometimes occur. Tends to lack objectivity—the ability to maintain a detached and rational perspective. Decision-making is challenging, with difficulties logically weighing the pros and cons. Communicates from the heart while demonstrating compassion and care through a strong intuitive nature. Personal relationships are highly valued, often resulting in the adoption of a caretaker role. This sympathetic and understanding nature, reminiscent of a maternal role, is counterbalanced by difficulty in maintaining objectivity, occasionally leading to impulsive reactions without prior reflection. Tends to flit from one pursuit to another, finding it challenging to settle down. Although change is welcomed, the stability needed to see projects through to completion is lacking. May engage in procrastination and expects others to exhibit flexibility comparable to personal tendencies. Receptive to others and sensitive to the subtle dynamics inherent in interpersonal relationships. Strives to make a distinct mark on the world. While this ambition can be beneficial, an overemphasis on idealistic pursuits may become disruptive. Reveals a strong connection between emotion and physical well-being coupled with a desire for perfection and order. Under stress, occasional health challenges may emerge. Exemplifies imagination, serenity, and creative sensitivity. Requires regular outlets for artistic expression and reflective time; intuitive and gentle, this personality gravitates toward dreamy, idealistic environments. Exhibits strong intuitive sensibilities and a vivid imagination. Often perceives subtle nuances in communication, though may sometimes blur the borders between reality and fantasy. Desires an almost transcendent unity with a partner, seeking a merging of individual and universal experiences. Finds fulfillment in inspirational and artistic shared pursuits. Exhibits a strong drive to defend and support causes or loved ones, while tending to withdraw when personally hurt. Values the continuous exchange of information and demonstrates versatility in both learning and teaching methods. Takes pride in work and builds personal authority, consistently striving for recognition and leadership. Drives transformative change through intense emotional focus and a dynamic approach to power and regeneration. Inspires with broad spiritual vision and expansive perspectives, encouraging inclusiveness in philosophical and religious views. Brings transformative change to interpersonal and global relationships, emphasizing the need for justice and recalibration of connections. A lively initiative and pioneering spirit are evident, marked by a direct, energetic approach to life’s challenges. There is an innate desire to lead, value challenges, and test physical and mental boundaries, balanced by the need to see long-term projects through to completion while managing impulsivity for safety. Professional success is achieved through conscientious, responsible, and authoritative conduct. Early setbacks may occur, but perseverance ultimately leads to widespread respect and recognition.
5002	Bubba Cascio	1932	Nurturing, protective, and tenacious, with pronounced emotional sensitivity and deeply rooted foundations. At times, may be overly protective, reluctant to let go, timid, or reclusive. Self-confident, generous, and warm-hearted, with strong leadership qualities and a dramatic presence. May occasionally appear overly proud, vain, extravagant, or arrogant. Even-handed, harmonious, and artistic, with a diplomatic manner and a strong sense of fairness. May at times be overcompromising, excessively appeasing, or judgmental. Enjoys challenge and action, becoming frustrated when no avenue for change exists. Expects others to rise to challenges as well. Finds it difficult to adapt to new situations and tends to be inflexible when faced with the demands of change or the needs of others. Seeks relationships from an objective standpoint rather than a personal one and values public engagement alongside contributing to society. Interactions with others assume a paramount role, with significant value placed on both personal relationships and broader social connections. Possesses a natural aptitude for mediation, informed by an understanding of the nuances inherent in relationships. The greatest insights into personal identity are often gained through these relational contexts. Care should be taken to avoid becoming entangled in stifling relationships. Public life is regarded as the pinnacle of achievement, with personal satisfaction derived from notable accomplishments and ongoing contributions in the public arena. A high public profile may be attained through career success and social status, though it is essential that such accomplishments do not come at the expense of personal relationships. Prioritizes harmony and peaceful surroundings, consistently seeking balance, especially during stressful times. Radiates warmth, generosity, and a fun-loving spirit. Naturally attracts attention through contagious enthusiasm and a playful, confident demeanor that uplifts those around. Boasts a highly analytical, detail-oriented mind with a preference for precision in communication. While sometimes becoming absorbed in minutiae, this quality is an asset in research and problem-solving. Places great importance on forming deep, nurturing bonds. Values family and an emotionally secure environment, with an underlying desire for stability in all aspects of life. Exhibits a strong drive to defend and support causes or loved ones, while tending to withdraw when personally hurt. Radiates benevolence, generosity, and a fun-loving spirit while actively seeking creative self-expression and a joyful environment. Works well in group settings, contributing original and innovative ideas while valuing collaboration. Embodies initiative and spontaneity, catalyzing the breakdown of outdated structures in favor of innovative new ideas. Integrates spiritual insights into daily routines with an emphasis on health, order, and systematic approaches to the mystical. Represents the upheaval and reformation of familiar systems, prompting new social concepts and security structures. A cautious, disciplined approach to life is typical, with an emphasis on careful planning and the steady pursuit of ambitions. Persistence, prudence, and a serious, reserved demeanor contribute to an attainable and respected path built through hard work. A career emphasizing beauty, harmony, and balanced interactions is attractive. Social skills and the creation of a cooperative and aesthetically pleasing work environment are valued.
5003	David William Crews	1933	Humanitarian and innovative with a strong group orientation and progressive drive to serve others. In some cases, rebellious, eccentric, aloof, emotionally superficial, or overly extroverted behaviors may appear. Displays objectivity and philosophical insight, favoring an intellectual perspective in approaching life. The rational mind consistently outweighs emotional considerations, which are viewed as less reliable. Possesses a strong sense of fairness and logical thought, though there is a tendency to consider emotions in a disparaging light. Emotional balance appears disrupted. The idea of exhibiting overt emotional responses, such as tearfulness or loss of composure, is highly discomforting. Compassion in interpersonal relationships may be insufficient, indicating a need to honor both personal feelings and those of others. Prefers to follow in others’ footsteps rather than initiate actions. Can be relied on to produce results as long as initial ideas are provided by others. Survival mechanisms are weak. May engage in procrastination and expects others to exhibit flexibility comparable to personal tendencies. Seeks relationships from an objective standpoint rather than a personal one and values public engagement alongside contributing to society. Public life is regarded as the pinnacle of achievement, with personal satisfaction derived from notable accomplishments and ongoing contributions in the public arena. A high public profile may be attained through career success and social status, though it is essential that such accomplishments do not come at the expense of personal relationships. Displays an emotional need for adventure, independence, and exploration. Under stress, tends to seek out new and invigorating experiences. Embraces unconventionality, innovation, and friendly, forward-thinking qualities. Thrives in group settings and relishes breaking traditional boundaries while expressing individual originality. Exhibits strong intuitive sensibilities and a vivid imagination. Often perceives subtle nuances in communication, though may sometimes blur the borders between reality and fantasy. Values unconventional, freedom-based partnerships that allow for strong individual expression. Enjoys intellectual connections and thrives in group social settings. Pursues objectives in a practical, methodical manner and may adopt a critical approach when facing opposition. Displays a profound desire to be of service coupled with high ideals and a strong attention to detail in all pursuits. Works well in group settings, contributing original and innovative ideas while valuing collaboration. Embodies initiative and spontaneity, catalyzing the breakdown of outdated structures in favor of innovative new ideas. Integrates spiritual insights into daily routines with an emphasis on health, order, and systematic approaches to the mystical. Represents the upheaval and reformation of familiar systems, prompting new social concepts and security structures. Versatility, adaptability, and a dynamic exchange of ideas define this approach to life. There is a strong emphasis on intellectual stimulation and communication, supported by an innate restlessness that fuels continuous learning and the pursuit of varied interests. Ingenuity and originality shape career choices, with a tendency toward unconventional professional roles. A strong desire to make a positive contribution to society may result in career changes over time.

Disciplined, responsible, and reliable, displaying industrious, conscientious, and practical traits that foster achievement. Nonetheless, tendencies toward pessimism, conventionality, rigidity, materialism, or callousness may be evident. Communicates from the heart while demonstrating compassion and care through a strong intuitive nature. Personal relationships are highly valued, often resulting in the adoption of a caretaker role. This sympathetic and understanding nature, reminiscent of a maternal role, is counterbalanced by difficulty in maintaining objectivity, occasionally leading to impulsive reactions without prior reflection. Strives to make a distinct mark on the world. While this ambition can be beneficial, an overemphasis on idealistic pursuits may become disruptive. Exhibits a self-motivated, self-oriented nature characterized by independently mapping out life and following an individual path, encountering difficulties only when impeded by external forces. Values independence and enjoys solitary pursuits as well as the company of others, provided ample freedom is maintained. Caution is advised against egocentric and selfish behavior. Values intellectual engagement over emotional expression and sometimes displays emotional detachment or skepticism regarding unpredictability. Displays optimism, enthusiasm, and a love for adventure and exploration—be it through travel or intellectual pursuits. Constantly driven by fresh ideas and a desire for continuous growth, this disposition pursues new goals with vigor. Is recognized for a wise, cautious mindset that prioritizes credibility and authoritative knowledge. New ideas are approached with deliberate care. Yearns for deep, soulful connections marked by emotional and sexual intensity. Pursues profound unity and shared transformative experiences in relationships. Channels a strong drive for spiritual exploration and is guided by deep, subconscious sensitivity. Intuition plays a central role, though there can be a tendency to adopt a withdrawn stance in threatening situations. Exhibits an intense, transformative quest for truth that is matched by a deep desire for profound connections and collaborative achievements. Cultivates lasting, responsible relationships through commitment and balance in both personal and business spheres. Promotes exploration of the unconscious and intuitive realms, leading to profound insights and creative breakthroughs. Infuses creativity with spirituality, manifesting dramatic artistic expression and an appreciation for aesthetics. Represents the upheaval and reformation of familiar systems, prompting new social concepts and security structures. A cautious, disciplined approach to life is typical, with an emphasis on careful planning and the steady pursuit of ambitions. Persistence, prudence, and a serious, reserved demeanor contribute to an attainable and respected path built through hard work. An intense, investigative approach to work is seen, with occasional crises serving as a catalyst for deep exploration and transformative insights in research and resource management.

Inspiring, with a broad vision, enthusiasm, and goal-seeking drive. Truthfulness and adventurousness define the approach; however, recklessness, lack of restraint, or tactlessness may also emerge. Strives to make a distinct mark on the world. While this ambition can be beneficial, an overemphasis on idealistic pursuits may become disruptive. Exhibits a self-motivated, self-oriented nature characterized by independently mapping out life and following an individual path, encountering difficulties only when impeded by external forces. Values independence and enjoys solitary pursuits as well as the company of others, provided ample freedom is maintained. Caution is advised against egocentric and selfish behavior. Public life is regarded as the pinnacle of achievement, with personal satisfaction derived from notable accomplishments and ongoing contributions in the public arena. A high public profile may be attained through career success and social status, though it is essential that such accomplishments do not come at the expense of personal relationships. Exhibits intense emotional depth and a strong need for profound experiences. Under stress, tends to generate or attract dramatic situations. Exhibits passion, intensity, and a deep engagement with life’s mysteries. Values honest, intimate relationships and is unafraid to explore complex emotional depths. Resourceful and insightful in practical matters, especially when overcoming challenges. Adopts a philosophical outlook that seeks to broaden perspective through continual learning. Values freedom of thought and clear, expansive communication. Demonstrates a strong need for harmonious, aesthetically pleasing relationships. Values creative expression and seeks balance and beauty in personal connections. Pursues objectives in a practical, methodical manner and may adopt a critical approach when facing opposition. Radiates benevolence, generosity, and a fun-loving spirit while actively seeking creative self-expression and a joyful environment. Is hardworking and practical with a strong aptitude for problem-solving; adheres to structure and discipline in daily and professional routines. Encourages brilliant, inventive breakthroughs that contribute unique insights to collective progress. Infuses creativity with spirituality, manifesting dramatic artistic expression and an appreciation for aesthetics. Represents the upheaval and reformation of familiar systems, prompting new social concepts and security structures. An open-minded, adventurous spirit is apparent, characterized by honesty, idealism, and a zest for constant discovery. A love for travel and a deep thirst for knowledge underpin life’s adventures, with irrepressible enthusiasm often inspiring others. A career emphasizing beauty, harmony, and balanced interactions is attractive. Social skills and the creation of a cooperative and aesthetically pleasing work environment are valued.

At times, self-confidence is insufficient even to set these goals, and a general lack of enthusiasm coupled with feeling overwhelmed by change is common. Displays objectivity and philosophical insight, favoring an intellectual perspective in approaching life. The rational mind consistently outweighs emotional considerations, which are viewed as less reliable. Possesses a strong sense of fairness and logical thought, though there is a tendency to consider emotions in a disparaging light. Enjoys challenge and action, becoming frustrated when no avenue for change exists. Expects others to rise to challenges as well. Seeks relationships from an objective standpoint rather than a personal one and values public engagement alongside contributing to society. Interactions with others assume a paramount role, with significant value placed on both personal relationships and broader social connections. Possesses a natural aptitude for mediation, informed by an understanding of the nuances inherent in relationships. The greatest insights into personal identity are often gained through these relational contexts. Care should be taken to avoid becoming entangled in stifling relationships. Displays a need for nurturing and comfort, tending to withdraw to secure, familiar surroundings under stress. Sometimes finds it challenging to break free from established comfort zones. Is serious, responsible, and methodical in pursuit of goals. Valued for reliability and a calm, steady presence during crises, this temperament is both ambitious and disciplined in achieving long-term success. Is recognized for a wise, cautious mindset that prioritizes credibility and authoritative knowledge. New ideas are approached with deliberate care. Favors adventurous, exploratory relationships, eagerly sharing new ideas and diverse cultural experiences. Enjoys dynamic, expansive partnerships. Approaches personal ambitions in a responsible and methodical fashion, demonstrating strong determination and occasionally assertiveness in defense of goals. Championing innovative ideas and inclusivity, exhibits a forward-thinking and humanitarian spirit. Is disciplined and logical, organizing details effectively and preferring clear, direct communication. Encourages brilliant, inventive breakthroughs that contribute unique insights to collective progress. Expresses spirituality with emotional depth and nurturing sensitivity, holding spiritual beliefs close to the heart. Represents the upheaval and reformation of familiar systems, prompting new social concepts and security structures. Versatility, adaptability, and a dynamic exchange of ideas define this approach to life. There is a strong emphasis on intellectual stimulation and communication, supported by an innate restlessness that fuels continuous learning and the pursuit of varied interests. Ingenuity and originality shape career choices, with a tendency toward unconventional professional roles. A strong desire to make a positive contribution to society may result in career changes over time.

May engage in procrastination and expects others to exhibit flexibility comparable to personal tendencies. Perceives independence and the ability to organize personal life, although self-centered tendencies may occasionally arise. Reveals a strong connection between emotion and physical well-being coupled with a desire for perfection and order. Under stress, occasional health challenges may emerge. Values intellectual engagement over emotional expression and sometimes displays emotional detachment or skepticism regarding unpredictability. Possesses a finely tuned, analytical mind that excels in tasks requiring concentration, organization, and rational thought. Values order in daily life and reliably handles both personal and professional responsibilities. Exemplifies diplomatic communication and serves adeptly as a mediator in interactions. Valuing harmony, prefers balanced and clear exchanges that foster mutual understanding. Favors fun, creative interaction and takes pride in the achievements of both self and partner. Maintains an appreciation for aesthetics, personal presentation, and a lively social life. Values harmony in action, combining a strong desire for justice with creative impulses, although situational indecision can emerge under pressure. Values the continuous exchange of information and demonstrates versatility in both learning and teaching methods. Shows commitment to higher learning and moral principles, balancing a strong ethical code with an optimistic work approach. Embodies initiative and spontaneity, catalyzing the breakdown of outdated structures in favor of innovative new ideas. Integrates spiritual insights into daily routines with an emphasis on health, order, and systematic approaches to the mystical. Represents the upheaval and reformation of familiar systems, prompting new social concepts and security structures. An open-minded, adventurous spirit is apparent, characterized by honesty, idealism, and a zest for constant discovery. A love for travel and a deep thirst for knowledge underpin life’s adventures, with irrepressible enthusiasm often inspiring others. A methodical, precise, and hardworking approach underpins professional life, with a focus on order, clarity, and high standards leading to recognition for detailed and exacting work.
5439	Kent C. Nelson	1937	Self-confident, generous, and warm-hearted, with strong leadership qualities and a dramatic presence. May occasionally appear overly proud, vain, extravagant, or arrogant. Intense and magnetic, possessing a penetrating perception and the capacity to confront challenges head on. Can display destructive tendencies, vengefulness, jealousy, or excessive drama. Highly motivated with many goals and aspirations for the future. Vital and spontaneous, this disposition often embraces the challenge of exploring new, adventurous paths. Enthusiasm is irrepressible, although there is a tendency to exaggerate and a difficulty in coping with routine tasks. Tends to lack objectivity—the ability to maintain a detached and rational perspective. Decision-making is challenging, with difficulties logically weighing the pros and cons. Communicates from the heart while demonstrating compassion and care through a strong intuitive nature. Personal relationships are highly valued, often resulting in the adoption of a caretaker role. This sympathetic and understanding nature, reminiscent of a maternal role, is counterbalanced by difficulty in maintaining objectivity, occasionally leading to impulsive reactions without prior reflection. Exhibits a marked aversion to change, while expecting others to demonstrate a similar reliability. Perceives independence and the ability to organize personal life, although self-centered tendencies may occasionally arise. Significant factors in this quadrant highlight the areas designated for self-expression. Exhibits a self-motivated, self-oriented nature characterized by independently mapping out life and following an individual path, encountering difficulties only when impeded by external forces. Values independence and enjoys solitary pursuits as well as the company of others, provided ample freedom is maintained. Caution is advised against egocentric and selfish behavior. Exhibits intense emotional depth and a strong need for profound experiences. Under stress, tends to generate or attract dramatic situations. Radiates warmth, generosity, and a fun-loving spirit. Naturally attracts attention through contagious enthusiasm and a playful, confident demeanor that uplifts those around. Boasts a highly analytical, detail-oriented mind with a preference for precision in communication. While sometimes becoming absorbed in minutiae, this quality is an asset in research and problem-solving. Places great importance on forming deep, nurturing bonds. Values family and an emotionally secure environment, with an underlying desire for stability in all aspects of life. Exhibits inspirational leadership and a profound drive for exploration and adventure, though sometimes maintains a singular focus in pursuing objectives. Demonstrates integrity by adhering to traditional values and working diligently toward professional success and recognition. Exhibits resourcefulness and applies innovative methods in practical ways, learning lessons of patience and self-reliance. Exemplifies tenacity in pursuing novel societal approaches, particularly in managing tangible resources and practical innovation. Integrates spiritual insights into daily routines with an emphasis on health, order, and systematic approaches to the mystical. Represents the upheaval and reformation of familiar systems, prompting new social concepts and security structures. A reserved and perceptive demeanor is marked by shrewdness and strong willpower. There is an ability to navigate complex emotional and public challenges with resourcefulness, with integrity serving as the keystone for achieving lasting goals. Professional pursuits are closely linked with personal pride and a desire to shine in the public sphere. Leadership, power, and strong organizational skills drive success in visible roles.
